HEADWORD: Pathfinder
<hw>Path"find`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who discovers
a way or path; one who explores untraversed regions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The cow is the true <qex>pathfinder</qex> and pathmaker.</q>
<rj><qau>J. Burroughs.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pathic</ent>⟦br⟧
